<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>٢٣٢- <span class="c2">«من رضي بقسمة الله.. استغنى»</span> .<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>٢٣٣- <span class="c2">«من رضي عن الله.. رضي الله عنه»</span> .<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
